title: Win Bobby’s Money + Bobby Addresses Negative Facebook Trolls

description:
A listener plays a round of trivia against Bobby in “Win Bobby’s Money.” Bobby addresses the negativity on the Bobby Bones Show Facebook page. Also, Amy’s son knows what he wants to be when he grows up.
